      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "This answer helped me a lot because <code>doAnswer()</code>/<code>thenAnswer()</code> do not allow chaining multiple calls as <code>doReturn()</code>/<code>thenReturn()</code> do and I needed to compute something and not just return a different value. Creating an anonymous <code>Answer</code> object with a private <code>count</code> variable was what did the trick for me."
