      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@KFleischer You CAN chain <code>doAnswer</code> calls, and also mix them with other <code>do...</code> calls.  You can also chain <code>thenAnswer</code> calls, and mix them with other <code>then...</code> calls.  I believe Lucio has made a mistake."
